{"address1": "Cello House", "address2": "8th Floor Corporate Avenue B Wing Sonawala Road Goregaon (East)", "city": "Goregaon", "zip": "400063", "country": "India", "phone": "91 22 6997 0000", "website": "https://corporate.celloworld.com", "industry": "Furnishings, Fixtures & Appliances", "industryKey": "furnishings-fixtures-appliances", "industryDisp": "Furnishings, Fixtures & Appliances", "sector": "Consumer Cyclical", "sectorKey": "consumer-cyclical", "sectorDisp": "Consumer Cyclical", "longBusinessSummary": "Cello World Limited manufactures and sells consumer houseware and glassware products in India and internationally. The company offers vacuum-insulated steel products, including flasks, bottles, sports bottles, kids' bottles, mugs, tiffins, soup and food jars, serving pots, and beverage dispensers, as well as hot pots, lunch packs, water jugs, single-walled steel bottles, and containers. It also provides opalware; and glassware, such as tumblers, hot drinks, storage containers, and mixing bowls. In addition, the company offers copper, including bottles, kalash matkas, glasses, coasters, and jars; insulated ware, such as water bottles, water jugs, hot pots, lunch carriers, tuff jugs, flasks, and chillers; and plastic houseware comprising storage containers, fridge bottles, dinner sets, plates, bowls, dry fruit sets, trays, bathroom sets, stools, and laundry baskets. Further, the company provides melamine; and kitchen appliances, such as mixer grinders, blenders, juicers, choppers, food processors, induction cookers, electric kettles, sandwich makers, toasters, OTG, and irons; and non-stick cookware, stainless steel, cast iron, and pressure cookers. Additionally, it offers moulded furniture including basic chairs, premium chairs, cafeteria chairs, center tables, dining tables, kids' tables, storage solutions; air coolers, such as desert, window, and personal air coolers; cleaning aids, including floors, sinks, ceilings, brushes, cleaning gloves, hand sanitizers, masks, and dustbins; waste management; pallets; extrusion sheets; tools and dies; and unomax writing, such as liquid ballpoint, gel, roller, fountain, metal ballpoint, metal roller, mechanical pencils, highlighters, markers, and gift sets. The company also sells its products online. Cello World Limited was founded in 1958 and is based in Goregaon, India.", "fullTimeEmployees": 5701, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Pradeep Ghisulal Rathod", "age": 60, "title": "Chairman & MD", "yearBorn": 1965, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Pankaj Ghisulal Rathod", "age": 58, "title": "Joint MD & Executive Director", "yearBorn": 1967, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Gaurav Pradeep Rathod", "age": 37, "title": "Joint MD & Executive Director", "yearBorn": 1988, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Atul K. Parolia", "age": 57, "title": "Chief Financial Officer", "yearBorn": 1968, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Sudhakar  Pawar", "age": 61, "title": "President of Sales (Trade)", "yearBorn": 1964, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Amitabh  Shukla", "age": 49, "title": "President of Sales (Non Trade)", "yearBorn": 1976, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Amit  Bhargava", "age": 57, "title": "Senior Vice President of Sales", "yearBorn": 1968, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mukesh B. Jain", "age": 56, "title": "President of Sales - Steel Category", "yearBorn": 1969, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Kaleekal Georgie George", "age": 61, "title": "President of Retail", "yearBorn": 1964, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Kamlesh  Devadiga", "age": 46, "title": "Business Head of Appliances & ECommerce", "yearBorn": 1979, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue":